<p>*Candidates securing 100% marks in SZABIST’s admission test will be equivalent to 50.</p>
<p><strong>For Masters Programs:</strong><br />50% score of GMAT for Master Programs</p>
<p><strong>For MS Programs:</strong></p>
<p>GAT (General) / HAT relevant with minimum 50% score OR GRE General with minimum cumulative score of 300.<u></u><u></u><u></u> <u></u></p>
<p>GAT General/HAT relevant is mandatory for MS students with minimum 50% score.</p>
<p><strong>For Phd Programs:</strong></p>
<p>GAT (Subject) with minimum 60% score / GRE (subject) with 640 score.<u></u><u></u></p>
<p>GAT (subject) is mandatory for PhD students with minimum 60% score.</p>
